{"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"OpenCL dramatically accelerates computationally intensive tasks by letting your application tap into the vast computing power of modern GPUs and multicore CPUs. Understand the OpenCL architecture and get all the details about OpenCL features in OS X Mountain Lion. See how auto-vectorization makes it easy for more apps to adopt OpenCL and gain specific insight into tuning your code for optimum performance."}],"metadata":{"modules":[{"name":"WWDC Notes"}],"roleHeading":"WWDC12","title":"Adopting OpenCL in Your Application","role":"sampleCode"},"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/wwdcnotes\/wwdc12-522-adopting-opencl-in-your-application"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"content","content":[{"text":"Overview","level":2,"anchor":"overview","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"😱 “No Overview Available!”"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Be the hero to change that by reading the transcript and providing notes! It’s super easy:","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"https:\/\/wwdcnotes.com\/documentation\/wwdcnotes\/contributing"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"minor":3,"patch":0},"kind":"article","hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/WWDCNotes\/documentation\/WWDCNotes","doc:\/\/WWDCNotes\/documentation\/WWDCNotes\/WWDC12"]]},"sections":[],"sampleCodeDownload":{"kind":"sampleDownload","action":{"identifier":"https:\/\/nonstrict.eu\/wwdcindex\/wwdc2012\/522\/","overridingTitle":"Read Transcript","isActive":true,"type":"reference"}},"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/WWDCNotes\/documentation\/WWDCNotes\/WWDC12-522-Adopting-OpenCL-in-Your-Application","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"references":{"https://nonstrict.eu/wwdcindex/wwdc2012/522/":{"checksum":null,"identifier":"https:\/\/nonstrict.eu\/wwdcindex\/wwdc2012\/522\/","type":"download","url":"https:\/\/nonstrict.eu\/wwdcindex\/wwdc2012\/52